headline: Divert, Inc. and PG&E Announce First-of-its-Kind Interconnection in California to Address the Wasted Food Crisis
summary: WEST CONCORD, Mass. & OAKLAND, Calif., November 21, 2024--Divert and PG&E announce a first-of-its-kind interconnection in the state of California to address the wasted food crisis.
